NAME

dattoascii - convert file from DAT format to ASCII

SYNOPSIS

dattoascii datfile asciifile

DESCRIPTION

dattoascii reads binary floating-point numbers from DAT-format file datfile and writes them in ASCII form to asciifile. Each vector is written as a separate line ended with a carriage return, with vector components within the line separated by spaces.

SEE ALSO

asciitodat(3) , QccDataset(3) , QccPack(3)
